==English==

===Noun===
'''ceremony'''
# A [[ritual]] with [[religious]] significance.
# An official [[gathering]] to celebrate, [[commemorate]], or otherwise mark some [[event]].
# Formal socially-established behaviour often in relation to people of different ranks.

